https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Vor/Tex downloads his consciousness into Tonys body and traps him in cyberspace.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Terminal Emulation
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: VOR / TEX steals Stark's body --trapping Stark in Cyberspace-- then goes on a rampage.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Iron Man and Vor/Tex clash while the Mandarin searches for his rings of power.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: While Iron Man and War Machine go toe-to-toe, the Mandarin prepares to end his time spent in isolation.
